  "keyFeatures": [
    "Header-only C++17 library for homomorphic encryption",
    "Arithmetic over 127-bit prime field (p = 2^127 - 1)",
    "Hypergraph-based encryption with public verifiability",
    "Support for addition, subtraction, multiplication operations on encrypted data",
    "Compact ciphertext size (42 KB fresh, 6-85x smaller than RLWE schemes)",
    "Fast scalar operations (2.9-14.3x faster multiplication vs BFV/CKKS)",
    "LPN-based security with 128-bit security level",
    "Text encryption and commitment support"
  ],
